These are Puzzles for 4x4 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-8-1::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: funk, house, indie, blues
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: siglo, cain, tiparillo, davidoff
The people have 4 different jobs:  architect, accountant, lawyer, scientist
There are 4 different favourite colors: fuchsia, black, orange, chestnut
 1. the accountant is not to the right of the architect##8
 2. the person who likes fuchsia is not to the left of the person who likes fuchsia##8
 3. the person who likes chestnut is on the far left or far right##3
 4. the architect is not to the left of the scientist##8
 5. the person who likes fuchsia is not to the right of the person who likes fuchsia##8
 6. the tiparillo-smoker is on the right of the scientist##1
 7. the fan of house is somewhere to the right of the fan of funk##5
 8. the davidoff-smoker is between the person who likes black and the accountant##2
 9. the person who likes chestnut is the tiparillo-smoker##1
10. the person who likes chestnut is on the right of the fan of blues##1
11. the fan of indie is on the left or right of the siglo-smoker##3
12. the fan of blues is somewhere to the right of the fan of house##5
13. the tiparillo-smoker is not to the left of the person who likes chestnut##8
14. the fan of house is the person who likes orange##1
15. the fan of house is not the accountant##6

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2     |      3      |    4    |
| Music-Genre         | funk     | house   | blues | indie |
| Cigar   | cain | davidoff   | siglo   | tiparillo  |
| Job         | accountant  | lawyer  | scientist  | architect |
| Color     | fuchsia    | orange | black     | chestnut    |

