.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-8-2::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  firefighter, police-officer, paramedic, librarian
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: september, march, december, august
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: aristoff, fonseca, vegafina, baccarat
House: wooden, gothic-revival, farmhouse, tower
 1. the vegafina-smoker is between the wooden house and the fonseca-smoker##2
 2. the police-officer is not to the right of the gothic-revival house##8
 3. the police-officer is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in september##3
 4. the firefighter is not to the right of the tower house##8
 5. the wooden house is not to the left of the fonseca-smoker##8
 6. the person who's birthday is in august is not to the right of the librarian##8
 7. the farmhouse house is somewhere to the left of the tower house##5
 8. the farmhouse house is in an odd position##4
 9. the aristoff-smoker is the gothic-revival house##1
10. the vegafina-smoker is on the left or right of the wooden house##3
11. the wooden house is not to the left of the vegafina-smoker##8
12. the librarian is on the left of the police-officer##1
13. the baccarat-smoker is somewhere to the right of the person who's birthday is in march##5
14. the fonseca-smoker is on the left or right of the vegafina-smoker##3
15. the firefighter is on the far left or far right##3
16. the person who's birthday is in december is on the right of the person who's birthday is in september##1
17. the firefighter is not to the right of the fonseca-smoker##8
18. the person who's birthday is in march is not to the right of the gothic-revival house##8
19. the librarian is on the right of the person who's birthday is in march##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |   2    |   3    |   4   |
| Job      | firefighter | paramedic | librarian  | police-officer  |
| Birthday          | august     | march | september | december  |
| Cigar   | fonseca    | vegafina  | baccarat | aristoff |
| House           | farmhouse | tower | wooden    | gothic-revival  |

