.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-8-3::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  pilot, scientist, dancer, firefighter
The people use 4 different means of transport: car, snowmobile, subway, taxi
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: january, may, july, june
There are 4 different nationalities: malaysian, pakistani, mexican, canadian
 1. the malaysian is on the right of the pilot##1
 2. the scientist is somewhere to the right of the dancer##5
 3. the firefighter is somewhere to the left of the person driving the taxi##5
 4. the dancer is somewhere to the right of the person who's birthday is in january##5
 5. the mexican is not to the right of the person driving the car##8
 6. the firefighter is not to the left of the person driving the subway##8
 7. the person who's birthday is in july is in an odd position##4
 8. the person driving the subway is on the left of the person driving the taxi##1
 9. the person driving the taxi is on the left of the person driving the snowmobile##1
10. the pakistani is on the far right##1
11. the person driving the car is not to the left of the person who's birthday is in may##8
12. the person driving the taxi is on the left or right of the pakistani##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2     |     3     |     4      |
| Job         | pilot    | firefighter   | dancer | scientist |
| Transport   | car     | subway  | taxi   | snowmobile      |
| Birthday   | may | january    | july      | june       |
| Nationality         | mexican    | malaysian | canadian   | pakistani    |

