.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-8-4::.
4 different games are played: go, bridge, poker, snooker
There are 4 different nationalities: egyptian, dutch, polish, argentine
There are 4 different favourite colors: light-blue, orange, black, yellow
City: liverpool, berlin, london, prague
 1. the polish is not the person who likes light-blue##6
 2. the person who likes yellow is on the left or right of the person traveling to london##3
 3. the person playing snooker is the person who likes black##1
 4. the person playing bridge is between the person who likes light-blue and the person who likes orange##2
 5. the polish is on the left or right of the person traveling to liverpool##3
 6. the person traveling to liverpool is not to the right of the person playing bridge##8
 7. the argentine is in an odd position##4
 8. the polish is somewhere to the right of the egyptian##5
 9. the argentine is on the right of the person who likes yellow##1
10. the person who likes orange is the person traveling to liverpool##1
11. the person traveling to berlin is not to the right of the person playing go##8
12. the person who likes light-blue is on the left or right of the person traveling to berlin##3
13. the polish is on the right of the egyptian##1
14. the person who likes orange is on the left or right of the person traveling to berlin##3
15. the egyptian is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |         2          |    3    |    4     |
| Game    | poker    | bridge             | go   | snooker     |
| Nationality   | egyptian | polish            | argentine | dutch    |
| Color     | orange | yellow | light-blue  | black |
| City   | liverpool  | berlin               | london  | prague   |

