There are 4 different favourite beverages: mirinda, almond-milk, coffee, milk
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: may, february, august, september
 1. the person playing scrabble is not to the left of the person who likes yellow##8
 2. the person drinking milk is the person who likes blood-red##1
 3. the person who's birthday is in february is not the person who likes yellow##6
 4. the person who's birthday is in may is on the left of the person playing backgammon##1
 5. the person playing scrabble is not to the right of the person drinking coffee##8
 6. the person who's birthday is in august is not to the right of the person playing scrabble##8
 7. the person who's birthday is in february is not to the left of the person who likes blood-red##8
 8. the person drinking almond-milk is the person playing domino##1
 9. the person drinking mirinda is not to the left of the person who likes turquise##8
10. the person playing backgammon is not to the left of the person playing scrabble##8
11. the person who's birthday is in september is between the person who likes turquise and the person playing domino##2
12. the person who likes yellow is on the right of the person who's birthday is in august##1
13. the person drinking almond-milk is not to the right of the person playing domino##8
14. the person who's birthday is in february is on the left or right of the person playing domino##3

.:: Answer ::.
