 9. the person traveling to hamburg is somewhere to the right of the person playing billiard##5
10. the person traveling to hannover is on the left or right of the person playing billiard##3
11. the person playing go is on the right of the person playing poker##1
12. the person playing billiard is not the person watching adventure movies##6
