 3. the owner of the ferret is somewhere to the left of the person who likes ebony##5
 4. the person eating pumpkin is the person who growsdahlia##1
 5. the person who growsmarigold is in an even position##4
 6. the owner of the ferret is somewhere between the person who growsazalea and the person who growssunflower##7
 7. the owner of the ferret is not to the left of the owner of the goat##8
 8. the owner of the hamster is somewhere between the person who likes pink and the person who likes brown##7
 9. the person eating kiwi is on the far left or far right##3
10. the person eating azaleamelon is not to the left of the person eating azaleamelon##8
11. the person eating kiwi is on the far left##1
12. the person eating cherry is on the far right##1
13. the owner of the ferret is the person who likes pink##1
14. the person who likes pink is not to the left of the person who growssunflower##8
15. the owner of the hamster is somewhere to the right of the person who growsdahlia##5
16. the person eating azaleamelon is not to the left of the person who likes purple##8

