 1. the person drinking soy-milk is the person drinking soy-milk##1
 2. the person who's birthday is in november is somewhere to the left of the person who's birthday is in february##5
 3. the person drinking hot-chocolate is somewhere to the left of the person drinking almond-milk##5
 4. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the left of the person who's birthday is in october##1
 5. the person playing scrabble is on the left or right of the person eating apple##3
 6. the person who's birthday is in february is the person who's birthday is in february##1
 7. the person who's birthday is in september is on the far left##1
 8. the person drinking soy-milk is on the left of the person playing monopoly##1
 9. the person playing scrabble is somewhere to the left of the person eating apple##5
10. the person eating apple is on the right of the person drinking almond-milk##1
11. the person playing monopoly is on the far left or far right##3
12. the person playing bridge is on the left or right of the person eating carrot##3
13. the person drinking 7up is not to the left of the person who's birthday is in november##8
14. the person who's birthday is in october is not to the right of the person who's birthday is in february##8
